          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-copy-10-1691492788141-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Spanish-style chicken breast & pepper stew</strong> over the<strong> cooked rice</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>garlic aioli</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
